Titolo: Hot Wheels: Stunt Track Challenge

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Hot Wheels: Stunt Track Challenge is a video game developed by Climax Racing and published by THQ. It was released in November 2004 for PlayStation 2, Xbox, and Microsoft Windows. It is the ninth installment in the Hot Wheels series of video games. A Game Boy Advance port was developed by Razorback Developments, implementing many elements from the home console versions.
The game received mixed reviews from critics upon its release.

Genere: Racing 

Valutazione: 62
